txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: flawed goo from the spiders to the west of Esteldín. Deliver the items to Ferrif within Esteldín.
'I will ensure that this is put to good use, thank you.'
'It may seem disgusting, but there is much that we can do with the goo that comes from the spiders. Collect some for us?'
Rangers of Esteldín Task: Flawed Goo
Ferrif, a Ranger, has asked for a collection of flawed goo to be delivered to him at the Ranger's home at Esteldín.
Deliver the flawed goo to Ferrif in Esteldín
You have accepted a task to collect flawed goo from the spiders in the area surrounding Esteldín to the west. Once collected, you are to deliver the items to Ferrif within Esteldín.
Wanted: flawed goo from the spiders to the west of Esteldín.
